<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The default text of Zend_Validate_Digits when validation isn't passed is the following:</p>

<pre><code>* '500.00' contains not only digit characters
</code></pre>

<p>An improvement might be something like:</p>

<pre><code>* '500.00' contains characters that are not digits; only digits are allowed
</code></pre>

